s://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1706231587/image_1706231587.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743759-tradeweb-exchange-traded-funds-update-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 10:10:00"}, {"id": "4743769", "title": "New Precedent Established For Politics To Drive Longshore Union Negotiations", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Truck carrying forty-foot container leaving port terminal with ship and quay crane on the background. Seaport operation activities, container shipping, and logistics.\" data-id=\"2157040201\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Kosal Hor</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Following President Joe Biden's intervention in October to end the brief strike at East and Gulf Coast ports, US longshore labor negotiations can no longer be seen through a traditional lens. The precedent now firmly established is that politics will</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157040201/image_2157040201.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743769-new-precedent-established-politics-drive-longshore-union-negotiations", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 10:00:00"}, {"id": "4743767", "title": "U.S. Importers Dabbling In Frontloading Ahead Of New Tariff Threat", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of containers and container ship in sea\" data-id=\"1008180456\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Michael H</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>US importers are better prepared for the imminent tariffs that President-elect Donald Trump has promised to slap on goods from China, yet the majority don't seem to be significantly rushing orders to get those goods across the docks ahead</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743767-us-importers-dabbling-frontloading-ahead-new-tariff-threat", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 09:35:00"}, {"id": "4743766", "title": "Allspring Special Mid Cap Value Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Growth, money growing\" data-id=\"1321347264\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gabriella Imperatori-Penn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The fund underperformed the Russell Midcap Value Index during the third quarter. Stock selection within real estate and consumer staples contributed to relative performance. Stock selection in industrials and health care detracted the most from relative performance.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321347264/image_1321347264.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743766-allspring-special-mid-cap-value-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 09:30:00"}, {"id": "4743758", "title": "InMode: Product Origination And Undervaluation Make The Stock A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medical expenses\" data-id=\"1216293549\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">gerenme/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>InMode Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INMD\" title=\"InMode Ltd.\">INMD</a></span>) reports impressive net income growth coming from the sale of non-invasive surgical products. The company recently delivered two more platforms, Define and Envision, which may bring further business growth in the future. In addition, the company's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1216293549/image_1216293549.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743758-inmode-product-origination-and-undervaluation-make-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 09:17:21"}, {"id": "4743752", "title": "Black Stone Minerals: Distribution Coverage Should Improve From Q3 2024 Levels", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil wells and power lines on the side of the highway.\" data-id=\"1750451788\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ugurhan</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Black Stone Minerals (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BSM\" title=\"Black Stone Minerals, L.P. Common Units\">BSM</a></span>) reported noticeably lower production <a href=\"https://investor.blackstoneminerals.com/news-releases/news-release-details/black-stone-minerals-lp-reports-third-quarter-results-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">in Q3 2024</a>, with an approximately 8% decline in total production quarter-over-quarter. This contributed to its distribution coverage (for a $0.375 per unit quarterly distribution) being reduced to 1.00x.</p> <p>I do</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1750451788/image_1750451788.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743752-black-stone-minerals-distribution-coverage-should-improve-from-q3-2024-levels", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:45:00"}, {"id": "4743754", "title": "IQVIA: Will This Beaten-Down Stock Bounce Back? 3 Things To Know", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image